  <processinfo id="aspace_a3e0c957f871f8d00d9ee132c2ba6cc3">
    <head>Processing Information</head>
<p>This collection was originally titled "Erasmus Hall Academy records" and combined BHS accessions 1977.377, 1978.113, and 1978.193. In 2023, materials from BHS accession 1985.054, BC accession 2009.0015, the Brooklyn ephemera collection (BCMS.0007), and the Brooklyn Collection clippings files were added as well and the collection was renamed to better reflect its contents.</p>  </processinfo>
